  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 263572,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " "
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263573,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうだ、これがスチールホラーの真の力・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's right, this is the true power of the Steel Horror..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263574,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "私も前にこういう状況になってさんざんやられて逃げるしかなかった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I was in a situation like this before, got thoroughly beaten and had no choice but to run away."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263575,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "太刀打ちはできない、今は撤退しよう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We can't stand against them, let's retreat for now."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263576,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "空飛ぶ戦車が来たらもっとやばいぞ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If the flying tanks come, it'll be even worse."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263577,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あれよりやっかいなのがいるのか・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Is there something even more troublesome than that...?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263578,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうだ・・それは・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Yes... that is..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263579,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "バラバラバラ　ヘリコプターの音が聞こえてきた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rattling sounds—the noise of a helicopter could be heard."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263580,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "この音だ、やばい、奴らが来るぞ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It's this sound, it's bad, they're coming."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263581,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ヘリが襲ってきて、ミラクルの武器を吹き飛ばす。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The helicopter attacks and blows away Miracle's weapon."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263582,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あああ・・魔法力が特大の貴重な杖が・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Aaaah... my precious staff with huge magical power..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263583,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "予備は・・この電磁パルスの杖しかない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "As a spare... I only have this electromagnetic pulse staff."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263584,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ランスと一緒に入った電卓迷宮で拾った物、パワーないのでゴミ武器だが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I picked it up in the calculator labyrinth with Rance. It's a worthless weapon with no power though."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263585,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ランスとの思い出だから持ち歩いていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I carried it because it’s a memento of Rance."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263586,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ないよりましかと電磁パルスの杖をふると・・キーーーんと不思議な音がした",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Thinking it's better than nothing, I swung the electromagnetic pulse staff... and a strange high-pitched sound rang out."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263587,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そして戦車が動かなくなり、ヘリもふらふらと落ちていった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then the tanks stopped moving, and the helicopter staggered and fell."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263588,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "何事だ・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What is happening..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263589,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "よくわからん、とにかくいまのうちに逃げよう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I don't understand, but anyway, let's escape while we can."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263590,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "戦闘が少し引いた所でミラクルは術を唱え異界ゲートをオープンする",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "When the battle subsided a bit, Miracle cast a spell and opened an otherworldly gate."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263591,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ミラクルが言う、わかっただろ、スチールホラーの恐ろしさが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miracle says, 'You understand now, the terror of the Steel Horror.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263592,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス、うむ・・・あれはやばいな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance: 'Yeah... that is seriously dangerous.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263593,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "健太郎と美樹が言う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Kentaro and Miki spoke."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263594,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ここが、僕たちの世界です",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This is our world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263595,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あんな恐ろしい世界から来ていたのか、さすが魔王だとミラクル納得",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So they came from such a terrifying world; Miracle was convinced, 'As expected of the Demon King.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263596,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "本当は危ない世界じゃないよ、こんなの変です",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Actually, it's not a dangerous world, something like that would be strange."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263597,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスさん達はすぐに向こうで喧嘩するから、ああなるんだよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Because Rance and his group always fight over there, that's what happens."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263598,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "こっちの世界だって悪い事したら警備隊に捕まるでしょ、一緒だよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In this world too, if you do bad things, the guards catch you—it's the same."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263599,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "・・・うむむ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "...Hmm."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263600,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "とにかく、戻ろうとするが",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anyway, they try to go back but"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263601,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "美樹がここに残りたいという",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miki says she wants to stay here."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263602,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "少し悩むが・・・わかった。残れ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After some hesitation... 'Alright. Stay.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263603,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "これまでありがとうと二人と別れを告げて",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They thank the two for everything so far and say farewell."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263604,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス達は異界ゲートを通ります。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and the others pass through the otherworldly gate."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263605,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "駄目だ、連れてかえる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No, I have to take you back."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263606,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "こんな危険な所に君を置いていく事は出来ない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I can't leave you in such a dangerous place."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263607,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "美樹もなっとくする、魔王のままでは帰れない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miki agrees; she can't return as the Demon King."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263608,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "やっぱり魔王、魔人を直してからで・・それにお世話になっているランスさん達に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After all, as Demon King, I'll fix the demons first... and besides, I want to help Rance and the others who've helped me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263609,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "協力したいからと残ります。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She stays because she wants to cooperate."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263610,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あっ、健太郎、お前はいいぞ・・ここにいろ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ah, Kentaro, you’re fine... stay here."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263611,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いやだよ、ぼくも一緒にかえるー",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No, I want to go back with you too!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263612,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス達は異界ゲートを通ります。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and the others pass through the otherworldly gate."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263613,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス達は異界ゲートから戻ってきた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and the others returned from the otherworldly gate."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263614,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス城。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance Castle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263615,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "やばい所だった・・やっぱこっちがいい、空気もいい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That place was dangerous... this is definitely better, the air is nice too."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263616,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あれがミラクルさんが恐れていたスチールホラーか、危険ですね。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's the Steel Horror Miracle was afraid of; it's dangerous, isn't it?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263617,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あんなのが攻めてきたら大変だ・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If something like that attacks us, it will be terrible..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263618,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いずれ対策を考えねばいけないが、今は魔人との戦いに集中しよう。うん",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We have to think of a countermeasure eventually, but for now, let's focus on the battle with the demons. Yes."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263619,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ミラクル",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Miracle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263620,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　・・・この電磁パルスの杖、もしかして対スチールホラーの切り札になるのでは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "...This electromagnetic pulse staff might just be the trump card against the Steel Horror."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263621,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　研究しなくてはと考えている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I need to research it, she thinks."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263622,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（ここは美樹を連れてかえる、かえらない、両方で使うので、美樹は出さないで下さい）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Here, since both 'take Miki back' and 'not take her back' routes are used, please do not display Miki.)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263623,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "・・・・・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "......"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263624,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そして数年後",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And then, several years later,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263625,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔人ケイブリスが支配する世界",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A world ruled by the demon Kaibris."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263626,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "怯えている、人類は支配下におき敵はいなくなったが、魔王が見つかっていない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Terrified, humanity is under control and there are no enemies, but the Demon King has not been found."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263627,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "探せ、探せと・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Search, search for him..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263628,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そこに報告・・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Then a report arrives..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263629,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔王リトルプリンセスが現れました。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The Demon King Little Princess has appeared."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263630,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "天空より機械の兵団を引き連れて・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Leading an army of machines from the sky..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 263631,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "\t\t数ヶ月後、人類は負けた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "        Several months later, humanity was defeated."
    }
  ]
}

